ar Union POSTWAR INFLATION CAN PROVE NATIONALLY RUINOUS RUINOUS UNCONTROLLED in Hation can hit this country as in the comparatively recent past it has hit other countries when we have too much money to spend and not suf ficient commodities with which to meet buyer demand The danger of inflation wili not have passed with the firing of the last shot on the battle fronts It wiil not have passed until reconverted American indus try is able to meet the tremen dous peacetime demand created by four years of doing without and the purchasing power produced by ex cessive wartime earnings That hoarded up purchasing power rep resents many billions of dollars To do such a job industry must have tools and materials American industry cannot have these requisites if our first job is to be that of providing for the rehabilitation of Europe as European nations are insisting we must do and as we are at tempting to do Lawrence Sullivan in a detailed article in Nations Business points out that there remains of unexpend ed lendlease appropriations a total of 21 billions of dollars The law provides that"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-04-13T06:35:10.538Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89075140/1945-08-30/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_cedric_ver01:data:sn89075140:00516993352:1945083001:0097/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=403&w=288", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_cedric_ver01:data:sn89075140:00516993352:1945083001:0097/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=807&w=576", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_cedric_ver01/data/sn89075140/00516993352/1945083001/0097.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wood", "united states", "ohio", "grand rapids"], "location_city": ["grand rapids"], "location_country":